Im trying to find the reason for my ad being rejected.  Both ads said rejected because it had a picture of a celebrity on it.  But only one had a pic of a celebrity.

Hi Ryan, I'm sorry to hear about the confusion with your ad rejection. The reason for ad rejection can vary, and it seems like there might have been a misunderstanding. I recommend checking the email you received from Ad Support for specific details on why each ad was rejected. If you believe there was an error, you can appeal the decision by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com. For more information on what to do next after an ad gets rejected, you can refer to this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next).
You're welcome, Ryan! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.
